description: Number of simple exactly-4-connected unlabeled n-node graphs.
comments: This counts graphs whose connectivity is exactly 4. However, the numbers are not correct: the smallest 4-connected graph is the complete graph K_5, so the initial terms are incorrect. See A086216 and A259862 for more information. - _N. J. A. Sloane_, Jul 08 2015
links: Eric Weisstein's World of Mathematics, k-connected Graph.
crossrefs: See A086216 for another version. See also A259862.
